{"tid":1626253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［雞蟲抵抗中資］叫雞都要愛港，愛自己人","createTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:13:19.000Z","uid":40250,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"82b1fbe0f428cf85901766109764606dee5b3295","tid":1626253,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:22:59.000Z","msg":"不再幫襯141支那雞<br />\n一係搵陀地1仔，陀地雙鐘，再唔係就搵ptgf<br />\n<br />\n拒絕送錢俾支那，拒絕外匯流失，消滅貿易逆差"},{"pid":"28177cd4f55f3df5f255ec221e5bab5e755b4fc1","tid":1626253,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:31:14.000Z","msg":"【行動】商戶蝕大本對政府怨氣重！大家係時候出手connect沉默的中小企！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n隨著政府不斷挑釁香港人，火上加油，導致抗爭越演越烈。<span style=\"color: red;\"> 反送中持續了一百多日，警察胡亂鎮壓，亂放催淚彈，對地區造成嘅滋擾，無人幫襯對佢地來講造成極大損失。<br />\n<strong>依家開始有唔少藍絲或扮中立嘅商人對政府及警察產生怨言。</strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">請大家利用呢個機會，廣泛向商戶宣傳，爭取商戶棄暗投明，企起香港人一方，或至少唔再支持政府、警察，以及港共保皇黨。</span></strong><br />\n請推我個post以了解當中嘅行動策略。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1625700\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1625700</a>"},{"pid":"03550eee9b1a5fe660deeb4ec17760a753b6628e","tid":1626253,"uid":197213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T10:32:41.000Z","msg":"有冇推介，想支持黃色生產業鏈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ff726ad59cfe36854ee9e7fcb1420a98e3973e1","tid":1626253,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T18:36:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c8aa4ed4c897dbeb28c8b95d91aacb83245c0d5b","tid":1626253,"uid":171506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T19:02:55.000Z","msg":"咩叫陀地1仔，陀地雙鐘<br />\n<br />\nPTGF又點搵<br />\n<br />\n求教學"},{"pid":"5647ef02f70b6f83e6c67e64640f28f6aa732f74","tid":1626253,"uid":13914,"like":