經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物/單據同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"3572b4b85225d1312122aacfcd6ac6c43f45439e","tid":1626253,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:56:32.000Z","msg":"性工作者平日比黑警食霸王食，受盡欺壓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f3dc65f4cc148190390ab0a8f3b6c9be2b2b96","tid":1626253,"uid":266100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T09:13:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}